{"tid":2346901,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"開始有爆煲新聞","createTime":"2020-12-30T15:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T16:18:40.000Z","uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6f616d564ca1f1a19393649b11c6a823a737cb93","tid":2346901,"uid":78492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"今早11時許，一名女子被丈夫發現在灣仔石水渠街1號一單位內上吊，大驚報案並將女子解下，救護員到場將女子送律敦治醫院搶救，惟至晚上醫生已初步判定腦幹死亡。然而警方深入調查後，認為案件另有內情，改列自殺及企圖謀殺跟進。<br />\n<br />\n目前母親仍在深切治療部搶救中，惟醫生初步已診斷腦幹死亡。至於7歲長子除了頸部有些許紅腫，未有大礙。<span class=\"red\">警方提到，該名母親沒有精神病紀錄，其家庭沒有家暴紀錄，亦非社工跟進個案，警方提到有關家庭因疫情關係，正面臨經濟困難。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201230/3X3RYFFMA5AOPDSJ4K7MFSX4TY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201230%2F3X3RYFFMA5AOPDSJ4K7MFSX4TY%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=c382de96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201230%2F3X3RYFFMA5AOPDSJ4K7MFSX4TY%2F&h=baabb8a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201230/3X3RYFFMA5AOPDSJ4K7MFSX4TY/</a>"},{"pid":"182e5b4af6f29879c13c75daae450bdd1e7be4c1","tid":2346901,"uid":223504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36aa72d477b90241f5bca811c2a160567b6f2c2","tid":2346901,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"功課難到自己都唔識，所以自殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6fbeb8bc865ea0364779d2043bfc94d30bebbb","tid":2346901,"uid":188322,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T15:23:41.000Z","msg":"大蕭條<br />\n啪啪啪<br />\n股災樓災陷球剷<br />\n啪啪啪<br />\n<img src=\"/ass